laboration, and increased successful post school outcomes.
Dreamchasers Pre-ETS program utilizes an innovative Blended Learning instructional methodology that leverages technology to provide a more personalized approach to learning. Participants receive programming in five areas:
-Job exploration counseling
-Work based learning experiences, which may include in-school or after school opportunities, experiences outside of the traditional school setting, and/or internships.
